data.description: **GREAT OPPORTUNITY! 2.75 % INTEREST RATE MORTGAGE IS ASSUMABLE** Welcome to the private lakefront cozy gated community of Emerald Cove! This beautifully appointed 2 story 3 bedroom + flex space, 2.5 bath, 2 car garage is everything you're looking for and more. Completely remodeled, no detail was spared. This home features a screened double glass door entry way, new exterior/ interior paint, all new exterior/ interior lighting, all new flooring throughout, new shower & tub, bathroom vanities, ceiling fans and a kitchen that will take your breath away. Large living area with sliders leading to the covered lanai will allow you the perfect space for entertaining parties of all sizes. Master bedroom located on the first floor offers privacy from your children and guests. On the 2nd floor, you will find 2 bedrooms, large bathroom and oversized loft overlooking the downstairs living room. Emerald Cove offers a heated swimming pool, picnic tables, bbq area, playground, long dock perfect for fishing or relaxing at the end of the day and a beach style lake featuring a pavilion available for hosting gatherings. This home is easy to show so schedule your appointment today!
